## [QuizFeedback](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/forms/quiz-feedback)

### Methods

|                                                 Method                                                 | Return type |                   Brief description                   |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|-------------|-------------------------------------------------------|
| [getLinkUrls()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/forms/quiz-feedback#getLinkUrls()) | `String[]`  | Gets a list of the URLs associated with the Feedback. |
| [getText()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/forms/quiz-feedback#getText())         | `String`    | Gets the Feedback's display text.                     |
